PirateHijack: 劫持
PirateNoCanDo1: 你倒是说说，你觉得我能拿这个干嘛？
PirateNoCanDo2: 我担心，恐怕无法劫持这个。
PirateNoCanDo3: 给我带来合适的暴击武器，懂吗？
PirateBroke1: 这不是免费的，你知道的
PirateBroke2: 给我整点宝贝来，如何？
PirateBroke3: 你是不是想来劫持我？你这混蛋！
PirateSuccessful1: 好了，伙计！跟新的一样！
PirateSuccessful2: 不支持退款！
PirateSuccessful3: 是的，伙计。
TravellingMerchantGiveWhetstone: 砥石
TravellingMerchantGiveWhetstone1: Here, I found these during my travels. You seem like a fighter, maybe you'll have a use for them.
TravellingMerchantGiveWhetstone2: Thanks for the tip! Here's something I found on my travels. Perhaps you can make good use of them.
TravellingMerchantGiveWhetstone3: I appreciate the money. Here, take these.
TravellingMerchantGiveWhetstone4: Cha-ching! Here you go! I hope these can be of some use.
TravellingMerchantBroke1: Everything has a price, even if I don't need it; I won't give these to you for free.
TravellingMerchantBroke2: Sorry, I can't give whetstones. Come back when you're a little... hmmmm... richer?
TravellingMerchantBroke3: What's that? Oh, you don't have any money. Scraggle off, pal!
TravellingMerchantAlreadyGiven1: That was all I had! I'll bring some more next time I come around.
TravellingMerchantAlreadyGiven2: These things don't grow off of trees, you know.
